snippet.title: Wizard's Adventure Trailer
snippet.description:
As a wizard, you are pretty powerful and also have a pretty powerful apatite! This game takes you on an adventure from a dark dungeon, to a lush forest, to a brisk and beautiful mountain top!
This game is brimming with platforming and plenty of magic missiles, but the best part of any story is the people you meet along the way!

DOWNLOAD  HERE FREE:
https://casem.itch.io/wizards-adventure

Trailer Music was Done by Parish Dawe! Check out his Instagram below!
